    "body": "Thanks so much for reporting this issue. I tried to reproduce the issue, but couldn't.\r\n\r\nAfter updating and building the latest version of Turbo-Geth, I ran these three commands against both Parity and TG:\r\n\r\n**For Parity:**\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0xa1e4380a3b1f749673e270229993ee55f35663b4\",\"0x0\"],\"id\":64}' -H \"Content-Type: \r\napplication/json\" http://localhost:23456\r\n\r\ncurl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0xa1e4380a3b1f749673e270229993ee55f35663b4\",\"0x19ea66\"],\"id\":64}' -H \"Content-Type: \r\napplication/json\" http://localhost:23456\r\n\r\ncurl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0xa1e4380a3b1f749673e270229993ee55f35663b4\",\"latest\"],\"id\":64}' -H \"Content-Type: \r\napplication/json\" http://localhost:23456\r\n```\r\n\r\nResults in:\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"result\":\"0x6c6b935b8bbd400000\",\"id\":64}\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"result\":\"0x1bcae3710c1638c06\",\"id\":64}\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"result\":\"0x39798f8e51d7a12\",\"id\":64}\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnd for Turbo-Geth:\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0xa1e4380a3b1f749673e270229993ee55f35663b4\",\"0x0\"],\"id\":64}' -H \"Content-Type: \r\napplication/json\" http://localhost:8545\r\n\r\ncurl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0xa1e4380a3b1f749673e270229993ee55f35663b4\",\"0x19ea66\"],\"id\":64}' -H \"Content-Type: \r\napplication/json\" http://localhost:8545\r\n\r\ncurl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0xa1e4380a3b1f749673e270229993ee55f35663b4\",\"latest\"],\"id\":64}' -H \"Content-Type: \r\napplication/json\" http://localhost:8545\r\n```\r\n\r\nResults in:\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":64,\"result\":\"0x6c6b935b8bbd400000\"}\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":64,\"result\":\"0x1bcae3710c1638c06\"}\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":64,\"result\":\"0x39798f8e51d7a12\"}\r\n```\r\n\r\nAs you can see both Parity and Turbo-Geth report the same values.\r\n\r\n## Debugging\r\n\r\nTo help me figure this out, perhaps you can provide some further information:\r\n\r\n### System information\r\n---\r\nGeth version: `geth version`  \r\nOS & Version: `Windows/Linux/OSX`  \r\nCommit hash:  \r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n---\r\nAlso, please run the same three commands above and provide the results below.\r\n\r\nAlso, may I ask you if your node is fully synced?\r\n\r\nHave you modified any of the source code yourself?\r\n\r\nAlso, can you provide the exact command you uses to start `turbo-geth`?\r\n\r\nCan you provide the exact command you used to start the `rpcdaemon`?\r\n",
